Various scripts for Mikrotik RouterOS (see internal descriptions to find out more)

To install a script named foobar from a file named foobar.script execute
system script add name=foobar source=[ /file get [find name=foobar.script] contents ]
on your Mikrotik device. To modify an existing script named foobar do
system script set [find name=foobar] source=[ /file get [find name=foobar.script] contents ]
